{"tid":599982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"異見人士楊建利 聯合國人權理事會發言　中方人員連環打斷發言","createTime":"2018-03-21T02:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T05:04:56.000Z","uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"247d8f00490a57f3d0bcef94862f3ae8fb3c2e72","tid":599982,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"中國異見人士楊建利，在日內瓦聯合國人權理事會發言期間，連接被一名中方外交人員打斷。 外電報道，定居美國的楊建利在人權理事會，質疑中共是否能夠在聯合國機構代表中國；他又提到大躍進、文化大革命等等，導致數以百萬計民眾喪生。 一名中國外交人員則指，楊建利的言論離題，他獲邀發言，亦嚴重影響人權理事會聲譽。這名中方人員接連打斷楊建利發言。"},{"pid":"21285796edf4f46fcc6887d1a0ba8e4093a9231a","tid":599982,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd1cde98263139fac972946d296d9c3796cfe8e","tid":599982,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"聯合國班友會理你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6363209ab22f3960e3d6976da503510789802f1","tid":599982,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"咁冇禮貌，果然係生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b54e0797e623a6597e77239eb8dc0b1aec3d6","tid":599982,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"講事實嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8331e4ade25ee67273fd2dded85caa7b7a91d25","tid":599982,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}